'''Beka Lewis''' was a [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel Alliance]] commando who served as [[Brion Peck]]'s second-in-command. The two had fallen in love, but Lewis was killed in a fight against a group of [[Mercenary/Legends|mercenaries]] who had been hired by the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]].<ref name="CO">{{JournalCite|3|Changing the Odds: The Adventures of Dannen Lifehold}}</ref>

